{"tid":1583774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"論罷買","createTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T09:22:45.000Z","uid":218615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2d0975ec82b11deeebaa33251a154660ee2c76","tid":1583774,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:26.000Z","msg":"經濟學家關焯照直言，市民在一周內選一天不消費，對本港整體經濟的影響不大，因罷買一天後仍需購物，只是將購買日期改變，完全不會影響企業的收入，要起到影響經濟作用微乎其微。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們應該做的是選擇性消費，拒絕向與自己持相反立場的商戶消費，轉而支持和自己相同立場的商戶。<br />\n<br />\n9月中，網民發現了制裁商戶的新方法，就是透過點擊搜尋引擎中的「廣告」，以增加點擊率，點擊率越高，廣告費就越貴。網民一呼百應，更因爲網友的瘋狂點擊，導致了士多Ztore 官方網頁的癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n與民爲敵，自然沒有好下場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105634690832571/posts/110987613630612?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105634690832571%2Fposts%2F110987613630612%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG16DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=dbd8e577\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105634690832571/posts/110987613630612?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d783a0e941238a50453da734735100eba96a0931","tid":1583774,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"05c70cd1369a77d7b2b2cbff7ec635ac556c5d3e","tid":1583774,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb8dc6c16aae1d2fd69298854636fbef9ecd033","tid":1583774,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:10:58.000Z","msg":"<span 